snippet.textDisplay: An absolute masterclass from a producer’s perspective, a bold attempt to let every instrument and voice breathe at full gain and strike with full velocity. It still stands as a benchmark for live recording, which was once the norm back in the days of Papon’s era but is now mostly lost, as modern producers hesitate to explore the unknown. Truly timeless.
snippet.textOriginal: An absolute masterclass from a producer’s perspective, a bold attempt to let every instrument and voice breathe at full gain and strike with full velocity.
